					<p>
						CES Group and EcoOpera Systems are proud to introduce EcoTrack, our flagship module of Energy Management and Information System (EMIS) software-as-a-service suite EcoCEO!  Designed to answer the question “How is my Building Portfolio Performing?”, EcoTrack provides clear performance metrics for comparing energy usage with national benchmarks and normalized historical performance.  EcoTrack is a complete Measurement and Verification (M&V) software tool that accurately measures energy savings based on advanced statistical modelling techniques, verifying the return-on-investment of energy management programs and upgrades.  Other capabilities include – utility consumption breakdown by energy, cost and emissions, full utility cost breakdown for bill verification, projected annual performance, savings and energy-use-intensity, portfolio buildings energy-intensity ranking, and energy-use daily, weekly and monthly profiles. 
